latestIgtvVideos.caption:

I’ve been doing this for over 2 years. Got from 3500 to 7000 authentic followers in less than 50 days. Previously owned a blog of 15,000 authentic followers. Also worked in a digital marketing company for over a year.

Needless to say, I’ve got a fair amount of experience in this field and on the way have discovered a lot of things that work and things that absolutely don’t. These are some of the basic things you should be doing for maximising your reach. If it helped, let me know in the comments. There’s other things that have worked wonders for me that I would absolutely love to talk about! :)
